TC_item.TC_Description: Triggers when ignition status is ON with upload permit function

LowBattery: The Electrical power manager for connectivity ask to A-IVC to warn the operator that system will soon don't have power left trough a notification. Notification at True when budget is under ThresholdWarningUser (Low battery notification for user). False when budget is more than this ThresholdWarningUser .

ConnectionAlwaysOnAllowed: The Electrical power manager for connectivity ask to A-IVC to warn the operator that system will not be able to stay in MQTT always on trough a notification. Notification at True when budget is more than Threshold MQTT (Always on still allowed). False when budget is under than Threshold MQTT (Always on are not allowed anymore).
